lead_paragraph: Another Mexican Foray is currently talked of at New-Orleans, and rumor is so far explicit as to indicate Tamaulipas, Leon and Coahuila, as the Provinces to be dismembered; and that forces for the expedition are rallying in that city and at sever al points in Texas.
